title: ZETA Reward Given Only to ZETA and ZUSD Pools
body:
While ZETA team is planning of other ways to increase value for ZETA, 
ZETA mined from pools that are unrelated to ZETA and ZUSD are more likely be sold and thus negatively impact the price. Considering TVL from unrelated pools do not actually benefit ZETA. This vote aims to reward only ZETA and ZUSD pools and remove rewards for other pools.
choices: Yes, reward only to ZETA and ZUSD pools
No, reward both ZETA, ZUSD, and other pools
No, reward both ZETA, ZUSD, other pools but reduce rewards for the other pools
author: 0x44D1eFe1Ad9e38fCc58e715F2b5fF598D1620C4e
